{"tid":778874,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陸駿光帶電鋸行藥房","createTime":"2018-08-14T04:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T08:45:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a19300ada40fffb3d810487ff7550337972ce4c9","tid":778874,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180814/20475675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475675&d=8wRfes4BNiqzHQc1cLrktgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5b570463\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180814%2F20475675&h=43b540ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180814/20475675</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月14日 <br />\n<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】陸駿光帶電鋸行藥房<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180814/large/14ec3p16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180814%2Flarge%2F14ec3p16.jpg&h=18caa8c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n陸駿光喺ViuTV劇集《Plan B》演惡人閻羅，佢日前去尖沙嘴拍惡搞片，拖完垃圾去垃圾站，再帶住電鋸去藥房買消毒藥水，仲用兇狠眼神望住店員，但對方冇反應。藥房職員大大聲問：「你係咪嚟做工程？」<br />\n<br />\n陸駿光同馮仁昭講：「閻羅冇離開過元朗，戲入面揸住電鋸，觀眾就會好驚，落尖沙嘴做實驗，原來啲人唔驚仲會笑，甚至冇反應，可能早排動漫節多咗人cosplay，啲人覺得搞緊笑唔係認真。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：馮仁昭  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】吳保錡為似八両金忐忑<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【馮仁昭四圍超】張偉文唱歌唔食嘢"},{"pid":"924c0a53df252f02a0aa6ad06003f7b4cea6a47d","tid":778874,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"因為plan b無乜人睇？"},{"pid":"504a5297ca581deb700881170385ee30f73cf232","tid":778874,"uid":81686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:45:45.000Z","msg":"佢身型著衫幾好睇"}]}